TEXT.S: Ageq Gaga mniq Sincuseyn Ceynsusyang ka alang Ageq. 49 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 151 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 93% niqan 140 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 7% niqan 11 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Tayal86%, Amis1%, Saysiyat1%, ni rahuq na o 5%.
